Tawangsari CT II, Gang Gayamsari, Karangwuni, Caturtunggal, Karang Wuni, Caturtunggal, Jogja

Consists of two floors with a modern industrial concept with a high facade that feels relieved.
Serves a menu of food such as dumplings, lasagna, grilled rice, and various cakes with prices ranging from IDR 13K to IDR 27K. Drinks also vary, from coffee, tea to kombucha with a price range of IDR 15K to IDR 28K.
